1
03:37:03,902 --> 03:37:05,569
Ironfoot.

2
03:37:08,073 --> 03:37:10,074
[SHOUTING]

3
03:37:16,456 --> 03:37:18,207
[ALL SHOUTING]

4
03:37:18,458 --> 03:37:19,458
[SHOUTS IN ELVISH]

5
03:37:25,715 --> 03:37:28,703
DAIN:
Hey, Thorin!

6
03:37:28,903 --> 03:37:31,176
Ironfoot has come!

7
03:37:37,060 --> 03:37:38,310
Who is that?

8
03:37:38,728 --> 03:37:39,978
He doesn't look very happy.

9
03:37:40,230 --> 03:37:42,981
It is Dain, Lord of the Iron Hills.

10
03:37:43,233 --> 03:37:46,035
Thorin's cousin.
- Are they alike?

11
03:37:47,028 --> 03:37:50,656
I've always found Thorin
the more reasonable of the two.

12
03:38:00,917 --> 03:38:03,836
DAIN:
Good morning. How are we all?

13
03:38:07,424 --> 03:38:12,845
I have a wee proposition if you wouldn't
mind giving me a few moments of your time.

14
03:38:14,097 --> 03:38:16,140
Would you consider...

15
03:38:17,755 --> 03:38:19,966
[SHOUTS]
...just sodding off?

16
03:38:20,728 --> 03:38:23,309
<i>All of you!
Right now!</i>

17
03:38:23,510 --> 03:38:24,760
Stand fast.

18
03:38:26,353 --> 03:38:28,150
Come now, Lord Dain.

19
03:38:28,653 --> 03:38:30,484
Gandalf the Grey.

20
03:38:32,157 --> 03:38:34,761
Tell this rabble to leave...

21
03:38:34,962 --> 03:38:37,618
...or I'll water
the ground with their blood!

22
03:38:40,598 --> 03:38:44,835
There is no need for war
between Dwarves, Men and Elves.

23
03:38:45,086 --> 03:38:49,223
A legion of Orcs march on the Mountain.
Stand your army down.

24
03:38:49,473 --> 03:38:52,134
I will not stand down before any Elf.

25
03:38:52,844 --> 03:38:55,846
Not least this faithless Woodland sprite.

26
03:38:56,848 --> 03:38:59,892
He wishes nothing but ill upon my people.

27
03:39:00,977 --> 03:39:04,897
If he chooses to stand
between me and my kin...

28
03:39:05,867 --> 03:39:08,215
...I'll split his pretty head open!

29
03:39:10,209 --> 03:39:12,237
See if he's still smirking then.

30
03:39:14,449 --> 03:39:16,366
GANDALF:
Dain, wait!

31
03:39:17,744 --> 03:39:19,745
[ALL SHOUTING]

32
03:39:21,632 --> 03:39:24,750
Let them advance.
See how far they get.

33
03:39:25,168 --> 03:39:30,168
DAIN: You think I give a dead dog for
your threats you pointy-eared princess?

34
03:39:32,081 --> 03:39:34,343
You hear that, lads? We're on!

35
03:39:34,636 --> 03:39:37,262
Let's give these bastards
a good hammering!

36
03:39:37,514 --> 03:39:39,014
[SHOUTING IN DWARVISH]

37
03:39:39,891 --> 03:39:41,683
[ALL SHOUTING]

38
03:39:42,018 --> 03:39:45,812
Stand your men down.
I'll deal with Ironfoot and his rabble.

39
03:39:51,986 --> 03:39:54,696
Right then.
Let's get this done.

40
03:39:55,657 --> 03:39:57,282
Send in the goats.

41
03:39:57,617 --> 03:39:59,451
[DWARF SHOUTS IN DWARVISH]

42
03:40:09,254 --> 03:40:10,837
[SHOUTING IN ELVISH]

